{"type": "article", "id": 16819, "title": "Kevin Hviidcatch 蜂蜜包", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-30T07:20:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125502lwmjdUMHn47Vgxsr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款印上了黄黑相间的条纹的户外包名叫蜂蜜包，它可以沿着拉链拆成一条 5 米长的拉链绳，在急救时派上用场。蜂蜜包里面内置泡棉，可以直接抱着包在水里漂浮，里面套上了一个内袋，能够在拉开拉链时不让东西散落，也可以真正做到防水。这款用高拉力做的尼龙布料的包只有 700 克，却能承担 15 公斤的重量，另有一款橙色，<a href=\"http://www.zeczec.com/projects/catch\" target=\"_blank\">目前正在众筹。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261441201KwB0Vuhaq6tZxvr.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"426\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5325\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144120Ajv2QPRwVHOS75Nk.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"436\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144121NO3HGjqiMAQBoJ9n.jpg\" width=\"559\" height=\"672\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.20214669\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144122zbKSfJrOAYTq416U.jpg\" width=\"625\" height=\"684\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0944\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}